    		<hr>
    		<p>At McMaster, Engineering has always had a partnership with Nursing. We figure the guy/girl ratio in engineering pretty much matches the girl/guy ratio in nursing, so our parties get that much better if we invite each other. During frosh week, at social events, and at other events throughout the year, its common for engineering to team up with nursing to show the other faculties how awesome we can be together.</p>
